quran[4{c,v,t}:
9,37,"nasee to kufar mein aik mazeed kafirana harkat hai jis se yeh kafir log gumraahi mein mubtala kiye jatay hain kisi saal aik mahinay ko halal kar letay hain aur kisi saal uss ko haraam kar dete hain, taakay Allah ke haraam kiye hue mahino ki tadaad poori bhi kar den aur Allah ka haraam kya howa halal bhi kar len un ke buray aamaal un ke liye khushnuma bana diye gay hain aur Allah munkareen haq ko hadaayat nahi diya karta"
9,38,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumhe kya ho gaya ke jab tum se Allah ki raah mein niklny ke liye kaha gaya to tum zameen se chimat kar reh gay? kya tum ne akhirat ke muqaabla mein duniya ki zindagi ko pasand kar liya? aisa hai to tumhe maloom ho ke dunewi zindagi ka yeh sab srosaman akhirat mein bohat thora niklay ga"
9,39,"tum nah utho ge to khuda tumhe dard naak saza day ga, aur tumhari jagah kisi aur giroh ko uthaye ga, aur tum khuda ka kuch bhi nah bigaar sakuu ge, woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
9,40,"tum ne agar NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki madad nah ki to kuch parwa nahi, Allah uss ki madad is waqt kar chuka hai jab kafiroon ne usay nikaal diya tha, jab woh sirf do mein ka dosra tha, jab woh dono ghaar mein thay, jab woh apni saathi se keh raha tha ke"" gham nah kar, Allah hamaray sath hai"" uss waqt Allah ne is par apni taraf se sukoon qalb nazil kya aur is ki madad aisay lashkaron se ki jo tum ko nazar nah atay thay aur kafiroon ka bol neecha kar diya aur Allah ka bol to ouncha hi hai, Allah zabardast aur Dana o Beena hai"
